iti75:1.8:
"Na samaṇe na brāhmaṇe,
Na kapaṇaddhikavanibbake;
Laddhāna saṁvibhājeti,
Annaṁ pānañca bhojanaṁ;
Taṁ ve avuṭṭhikasamoti,
Āhu naṁ purisādhamaṁ.

iti75:1.12:
Evamevaṁ idhekacco,
puggalo hoti tādiso;
Dhammena saṁharitvāna,
uṭṭhānādhigataṁ dhanaṁ;
Tappeti annapānena,
sammā patte vanibbake"ti.
